<h2>Chapter 1: What the Data Actually Shows &#123;#ch1&#125;</h2>
<p>The only large-scale study comparing LLM scraped answers vs API results comes from Surfer SEO. Their data science team ran 1,000 prompt executions through both ChatGPT and Perplexity. They compared scraped web interface results against clean API calls using identical prompts.</p>
<p>The numbers are not close.</p>
